          "Holdout Method",
          "AST09\n{AUC: 0.848 - SAKT}\n\nAST15\n{AUC: 0.854 - SAKT}\n\nASTChall\n{AUC: 0.734 - SAKT & DKT}\n\nStatics\n{AUC: 0.853 - SAKT}\n\nSynthetic\n{AUC: 0.832 - SAKT}",
          "Authors also perform an Ablation study:\n\nThe loss in performance coming from positional encoding is not very pronounced.\n\nResults show that not only model performs better but is also1 ordder of magnitude faster.",
          "No Cross-Validation.\n\nCould explore more features and data from other sources."
        ]
