                "content": "Knowledge Tracing estimates the performance of a student in different learning activities, allowing it to model the student’s mastery of different knowledge concepts. The current state-of-the-art methods are BKT, DKT and Dynamic Key-value Mmory Networks and all have the issue of poor generalization in the rpesence of sparse data.",
